name: 原神[胡桃]-見世物編その1-えっち動画！
summary:
一个阴谋迫使胡桃承担了一笔巨额债务。根据合同，他不得不出卖自己来偿还债务。她被丑陋的男人轮奸，甚至被机器和触手羞辱。她被磨损的精神终于开始愈合，她为恢复正常生活而感到欣慰。她为恢复正常生活而松了一口气，但在短短的时间里，她听到了狂乱的脚步声，又有一个新的债主来了。另一个债权人来到了门前....她在大庭广众之下以尴尬的姿势被束缚住，被平彻羞辱，而街上的男人却在看着她，强奸她。请欣赏!

A conspiracy forces Oujodo to take on a huge debt. By contract, he had to sell herself to pay the debt. She was gang-raped by ugly men and even humiliated by machines and tentacles. Her worn spirit finally began to heal, and she was relieved to have her normal life back. She was relieved to have her normal life back, but in the short time she was there, she heard with wild footsteps, another new creditor arrived. Another creditor comes to the door.... She is restrained in an embarrassing position in public, and is humiliated by Hircher while the men in the street are looking at her and raping her. Enjoy!
